      "writtenOn": "2015-10-15T22:55:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good point.\nI\u0027ll actually make sure we retain the order as well as the comments (which we didn\u0027t do earlier).",
      "parentUuid": "df39c202_a73c0960",
      "revId": "3c2c56b6a225ba0ac507b7fb8f978a51786535f9",
